General.Name: NEXION Group Ltd
General.Description: NEXION Group Ltd operates as an information technology service provider primarily in Australia. It provides global network, compute, security, and data storage solutions as-a-service integrated with public cloud services to form the NEXION OneCloud, a hybrid cloud solution. The company sells its OneCloud capacity and technology management services to enterprise customers. It offers enterprise ICT managed services. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Perth, Australia.
